[ Upstream commit b0ff9b590733079f7f9453e5976a9dd2630949e3 ]

Add property "pinctrl-names" to swap pin mode between gpio and dpi mode.
Set the dpi pins to gpio mode and output-low to avoid leakage current
when dpi disabled.

